95
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:45,760
Let's actually walk through some of the things 
that you have learned about how to help people  

96
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:50,960
get good at these things, about how to help 
people learn to take a punch, AKA do hard things,  

97
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:55,920
deal with struggle. The first is you actually 
